Hey guys  There are two types of bug alt.  the early one had a big red wire 
and a 3 prong plug in on top  this type takes an external regulator  the later 
and replacement type only has 2 connections  a big hot wire and the dash lite 
wire and  has an internal regulator  these are bosch numbers Al82N   later and 
have fun  Mark Dearing
